  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: In release candidate `0.9.11` when I remove transaction on Sign transaction screen and close the screen I can see this transaction is shown in 1x1 chat as `failed` and `pending` in group chat\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nTransaction is not shown when I removed it and did not sign\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n1x1 chat\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/30583089-a4b42e1e-9d2e-11e7-94b9-fe4584ebfe49.png)\r\n\r\nGroup chat\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/28752642/30583104-b51dab90-9d2e-11e7-9c57-5591ce568688.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Add somebody as contact\r\n- Send txn in 1x1 chat / group chat\r\n- Delete this transaction on Sign screen\r\n- Pay attention to the chat\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: release `0.9.11` 0.9.10-103-g4672df2b+ (1660) \r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n* TF: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/6583606/sessions/11/?accessToken=3zuhuKI2ABGFcvXMxEDN8jwtlsc (from 0:42)\r\n",
